entries.femaleVariant: I sure as shit hope I don't run flat into some FIA snoop.
entries.maleVariant: Sure as shit hope I don't run flat into some FIA snoop.

entries.femaleVariant: Maybe I mask up – I mean, Reed does know my face.
entries.maleVariant: Maybe I mask up? I mean, Reed does know my face.

entries.femaleVariant: FIA'd tag you by the tech's sig as you went through security. It's their gear, they'd finger it anywhere.
Obviously, you can't be packing when you go in.
Black clinic, 'member? It's on Luna. Got a flight all lined up to get me there.
[Take the wheel] Rest up.
V.
Thinkin' back to that first contact you made? We've come a long way…
entries.maleVariant: Thinkin' back to that first contact you made – we've come a long way…

entries.femaleVariant: Haven't quite reached its end yet.
Ah, fuck – flashback comin' in hard. Konpeki Plaza heist.
entries.maleVariant: Aw, fuck – flashback comin' in hard. Konpeki Plaza heist.

entries.femaleVariant: Banish that shit. You're better than you were. Armed or not, you'll manage.
Yeah.
entries.maleVariant: Yeah?

entries.femaleVariant: Good luck.
Join up soon.
[Get out] See you soon.
Hey, V?
Have to behave like puppybots set to easy obedience mode.
…ditch this town.
Doe'n't matter at all, trust me.
Standard spaceport security. Leave your iron with me.
Can't help but regret…
Help me…
FIA's gonna get us – that was his threat.
[Open] So Mi?
Any way I can help?
Wanna flee? Condition you're in?
Wanna flee, condition you're in? Won't get far.
Wanna help – tell me how.
Doe'n't matter what he said. Forget it.
Knew he'd try to intimidate, knew you'd blow 'im off.
Don't stop and talk, make eye contact, linger or look aimless. You have a terminal and gate to get to.
Just act normal. Like any other passenger.
So, what's your super spy secret for bein' invisible, movin' on the sly?
Should I mask up? Could help.
Got any advice, of the tradecraft variety?
Sorry you had to wait…
Sorry to make you wait…
My head's a cage full of pain… Agh.
I'll have it when we meet up again.
Just go.
They're agents of a foreign government operating in the Free City – illegally.
Yeah?
I don't wanna die.
I just…
Stubborn old bastard…
Stubborn old bastard… Reed.
Poke long enough, you could drill a hole…
Needed to prep.
Talked to Reed.
Just thought it was a good idea to prep.
So, what now?
So, yeah, talked to Reed.
entries.maleVariant: So, yeah, I talked to Reed.

entries.femaleVariant: Huh. And?
Ah, bit of lecturin', a few FIA-backed threats thrown in  – you know the drill.
entries.maleVariant: Bit of lecturing, a few FIA-backed threats thrown in  – you know the drill.

entries.femaleVariant: Ah, "negotiating by the book" – that's what everybody at the firm called it.
Hh, let's roll.
So, got a plan after all.
You're hurting. Think you'll manage?
Seems you've got a plan after all, to help us both.
entries.maleVariant: Seems you got a plan after all, to help us both.

entries.femaleVariant: Don't look so hot. Think you'll manage?
Now, I can't just stride in. I'd draw attention from who knows who in my condition.
Easy-peasy, sounds like.
Spaceport's got solid Orbital Air security.
This just might work.
What about spaceport security?
I…
Reed…
[Give injection] Hold tight.
Relax. All good.
Agh!
Need to buck up for this.
[Comfort Songbird] You'll be fine. Things'll work out.
Meds're kickin' in. You're all right.
Song, need to keep your shit together.
So again, Tycho Terminal – get there unnoticed by anyone who matters.
Eyes peeled for Orbital Air guards especially. We can't know what they'll be watching for.
We shouldn't linger.
Grab the wheel – could you?
Terminal closure – how'd you manage to get around it?
Said Tycho Terminal's closed for refurbishment. Sure you can fly out of there in spite?
Got a one-way ticket… from someone who follows their own rules.
All this shit's… too much.
No idea.
Think so.
Think not.
Dunno.
Expect it's hard as hell, but yeah, possible.
entries.maleVariant: Expect it's hard as hell… but yeah, possible.

entries.femaleVariant: Think not, no way.
I don't know, either.
[Hand over weapons] If I gotta, I gotta.
[Hand over weapons] Fuck meee… Reminds me of somethin'.
Steel yourself. We'll be pullin' in.
Also minimal security, probably. Can't ignore that factor.
Tycho Terminal's being renovated, so not many bodies, lots of cover…
So you'll stride in. Then head to the Tycho Terminal, find a side door to open for me.
Gonna help me out, think you can?
Save your strength, I'll manage.
Aa-argh...
Booster, V!
Full on netrunning – maybe via your personal.
Think you'll have the strength to netrun?
Think I can manage. You use the time well, to rest.
entries.maleVariant: Think I can manage. Use the time well, to rest.

entries.femaleVariant: I'll try. But let me know if you need me to link up, hit the net.
Try 'n' rest up.
Fuck, you look pretty, um…
V…? Ngh.
Hey!
Careful!
V!
What the hell're you doing?!
Aghrrr!
Spaceport's behind us, you know.
Are you lost? Use the nav set.
Uhp. Mighta made a wrong turn.
entries.maleVariant: Huh. Mighta made a wrong turn.

entries.femaleVariant: Don't fuck with me.
Sorry, I'll figure it out. Get us there soon.
entries.maleVariant: Sorry, I'll... figure it out. Get us there soon.

entries.femaleVariant: We don't need this kind of attention!
Shit, shit, shit!
Lose the tail!
Where the hell'd you go? What'd you do?
What the hell took so long?
Reed cares about you, truly.
A skilled manipulator if you ask me.
Think Reed cares about you, truly.
Wouldn't call what happened negotiating by the book. No, Reed goes for the jugular.
Has a use for me, maybe... but one use only – to feel good about himself, what he's doin'.
So young yet so jaded…
You're so tiny, said the picobot to the nanomech…
Unrivaled in that, yeah.
That'll depend heavily... on you.
I do. An' it relies heavily if not wholly on you.
Damn, V… I've wronged so many, hurt so many…
Hm.
With you on that.
Our deal's our deal, and it's solid.
Anything new? Anything at all?
Hung up on 'im.
He seemed expectant – for me to throw in the towel. Hung up on his ass.
Came straight here.
Came as fast as I could.
Pain made it seem like forever to me. Anything specific keep you?
Think you might be too weak to netrun solo.
Lemme share my personal with you.
entries.maleVariant: Lemme share my personal with ya.

entries.femaleVariant: Johnny did a number on Rogue.
Do my best not to hurt Judy.
I hurt Judy.
Sure hope I won't hurt Panam.
Try hard as hell not to hurt River.
Fucked up, hurt River.
Try hard not to hurt Kerry.
I did Kerry wrong.
Peeps or felines?
Don't often get the chance to right a wrong. But... when you do, you do your damndest not to fuck up again.
entries.maleVariant: Don't often get the chance to right a wrong. But when you do, you do your damndest not to fuck up again.

entries.femaleVariant: Someone revealed their secrets, revealed themselves to me.
Doe'n't take much to screw up. A careless word, misunderstanding, bad morning…
entries.maleVariant: Doesn't take much to screw up. A careless word, misunderstanding, bad morning…

entries.femaleVariant: Sometimes... just gotta do your damndest not to hurt that one soul you care most deeply about.
entries.maleVariant: Sometimes... just gotta do your damndest not to hurt the one soul you care most deeply about.

entries.femaleVariant: For some, for many, heh, the simplest truths are the weightiest.
entries.maleVariant: For some, heh, for many, the simplest truths are the weightiest.

entries.femaleVariant: Some peeps you get to hurt just the one time.
Some people expect more than you're prepared to give.
Lesson one – don't automatically run when things heat up.
Mm, my cat'd say it's possible. Then again, he only knows me, so…
entries.maleVariant: Hm, my cat'd say it's possible. Then again, he only knows me, so… heh.

entries.femaleVariant: [Jack in] Could run some diagnostics on you.
Lemme scan you. Need to know how you're doin', the state you're in.
Hm... shit. This isn't right.
entries.maleVariant: Huh... shit. This isn't right.

entries.femaleVariant: Can't hope to dive and hack, state you're in.
Whatever you want.
Degen's fast. Too fast for any known pathogen. Metastases spreading straight from the brain…
entries.maleVariant: Degen's fast. Too fast for any known pathogen. Metastases spreadin' straight from the brain…

entries.femaleVariant: I know what's wrong with me, V. Exactly why we need to hurry.
You've had shit luck with partners lately.
Till you came along… Workin' out kinda OK.
It's a burden, a duty. When a jewel's entrusted to you, you focus, don't lose it, find the strength not to disappoint.
Might cost you. Might cost you plain crazy heaps.
entries.maleVariant: Might cost you. Heh. Might cost you plain crazy heaps.

entries.femaleVariant: Need to take care, care not to lose folks. But that care, that caution is worth it, almost always.
entries.maleVariant: Need to take care not to... lose folks. But that care, that... caution is worth it, almost always.

entries.femaleVariant: Do that, and you lose all, you're left alone.
entries.maleVariant: Do that? You lose all, 'n' you're left alone.

entries.femaleVariant: Can be hurtful... to others, to yourself most likely, too.
Sufferin' comes in many different hues. Best sufferin'? Well, oxymoron, kinda, but it's over in a flash.
entries.maleVariant: Sufferin' comes in many different hues. Best sufferin'? Well, oxymoron, kinda, but... it's over in a flash.

entries.femaleVariant: You know, heh, you can lose someone by accident. It happens…
entries.maleVariant: You know, you can lose someone by accident. It happens…

entries.femaleVariant: Johnny'd have a thing or two to say on that topic. Too bad you two'll never talk.
Senses're goin'. Seein'… dark spots. It's ha-ard to breathe.
Not that way! Main entrance!
Wow, quite the coup.
Say wha'?
Could prolly use it.
Thanks. Could prolly use it.
It'll be fine.
Hey, Song – chin up, I'll manage. We'll manage.
entries.maleVariant: Hey, Song – chin up. I'll manage, we'll manage.

entries.femaleVariant: So, spaceflight means spaceport – NCX. It's where we're headin'.
Coup schmoo, it's my last resort.
Can't help wondering if it's even avoidable. You know… hurting others?
Goin' with you.
Uh, wanna go with you.
No, V, impossible. One and only one – it's all they're expectin'. And it's just not open to negotiation.
In all likelihood, I'll serve as their lab rat once there.
AI's within the neural matrix, they're going to extract it. Create a prototype cure for us.
I'll contact you. As soon they're ready for us both, I promise.
Takin' your word for it.
Sounds risky as hell.
Ugh, don't love the idea. Smells risky as hell, for us both.
Well, be awaitin' word.
Well, any risk-free options're way out of reach by now.
No matter. What now?
What's it matter.
Hm.
